     A parallel incident beam exits the back side, but the ray just tangent   :
     to the edge of the sphere is refracted by 45 degrees to meet the axis.   :
                              :                  :                            :
     This example is all-refractive, and so no column for surface type is     :
     needed;  the default is refractive.         :                            :
